TY  - JOUR
T1  - Consistency of Higher Order Risk Preferences
AU  - Deck, Cary
AU  - Schlesinger, Harris
Y1  - 2014/09/01
PY  - 2014
DA  - 2014/09/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.3982/ECTA11396
T2  - Econometrica
